bIsTemperatureSupported: Whether Temperature can be used in the frame data
bIsIntensitySupported: Whether Intensity can be used in the frame data
bIsLightColorSupported: Whether LightColor can be used in the frame data
bIsInnerConeAngleSupported: Whether InnerConeAngle can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsOuterConeAngleSupported: Whether OuterConeAngle can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsAttenuationRadiusSupported: Whether AttenuationRadius can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsSourceLenghtSupported: Whether SourceLength can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsSourceRadiusSupported: Whether SourceRadius can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsSoftSourceRadiusSupported: Whether SoftSourceRadius can be used in the frame data. Only used for spot lights
bIsLocationSupported: Whether location in frame data should be used
bIsRotationSupported: Whether rotation in frame data should be used
bIsScaleSupported: Whether scale in frame data should be used
PropertyNames: Names for each curve values that will be sent for each frame
